Apa maksudmu?

00:12:35.680 --> 00:12:40.120
Maksudmu pacar?
- Benar, Rishi.. Pacar..

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:45.560
Istrimu belum sembuh

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:48.720
hubungan terakhirnya.

